__ Cantrip: Charity __________________________ Cost: 3 _______________________

Use:  cantrip charity < item >                 Material Component: any item
Use:  C charity < item >

The cantrip charity is a minor magic of the spheres of alteration/evocation.
As the cantrip is cast, the bard drops an item and hisses.  An immediate gust
of wind will hurl the item at high velocity to the charity room of the bardic
guild, where it will land unharmed on the specially padded floor.
